data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of WATERSET, one of the most sought-after neighborhoods in the vibrant Tampa Bay area! Built-in 2022, this almost brand-new home is a masterpiece of modern living, designed to offer you the ultimate blend of luxury, convenience, and comfort. This residence, a symphony of style and functionality, features 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, and a 2-car garage ensuring ample space for relaxation and privacy. This beautiful house is also eligible for USDA FINANCING, which will allow you to purchase this gem with 0% down. As you pull up to your New Haven, the paved driveway welcomes you with an air of sophistication, hinting at the elegance that awaits within. As you step through the front door, you will immediately notice the spacious, open-concept living area, the tiled flooring, and the 9.4’ high ceilings. If the kitchen is the heart of a home, then this one will steal yours. With granite countertops, 36" wood cabinets, elegant tile backsplash, and gleaming stainless-steel appliances, you'll feel like a chef every time you cook. And the thoughtful touches continue - from the breakfast bar to the recessed and pendant lighting, every detail is designed to elevate your culinary experience. Among all its perks, this immaculate home offers a large guest room and a full bathroom on the main floor for extra convenience. Upstairs you can find a wonderful master suite with a huge walk-in closet, a spacious in suite master bathroom with dual sinks, a water closet, and a glass-enclosed walk-in shower. Additionally, you will enjoy two spacious bedrooms with big closets and a shared full bathroom. Nestled in the embrace of Waterset, you're not just buying a home; you're investing in a lifestyle. Picture yourself enjoying the warm Florida sun at the community pool, maintaining your fitness goals at the state-of-the-art fitness centers, and grabbing a coffee at the neighborhood cafe just a stone's throw away from your front door. With miles of scenic trails, this community invites you to explore and savor every moment of outdoor living. The location is not just about the amenities within Waterset – it's about easy access to major highways, simplifying your daily commute to Tampa or Sarasota/Bradenton. Say goodbye to stressful travel times and hello to more quality moments spent at home. This beautiful home isn't just a house; it's a canvas for you to paint the story of your life. It's ready for a new chapter, a new family to call home. Welcome to Waterset – welcome home! Schedule a showing today and prepare to fall in love with your future. Your dream home awaits!!
